
<body>
	<div class="row" style="background-color:aqua">
		<div class="col-6">
			<div style="height:50px; background-color:wheat"></div>
			<div style="height:330px; background-color:darkkhaki"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="col-6" style="height:100px">
			<div style="height:60px; background-color:gray">哥倫比亞 雪之山莊園 花蜜瓜瓜 水洗 咖啡豆 -200g</div>
			<div style="height:170px; background-color: lightslategrey">NT$666</div>
			<div style="height:40px; background-color: lightsteelblue"><button>1</button></div>
			<div style="height:110px; background-color: slategray">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-3">
						<button>加入購物車</button>
					</div>
					<div class="col-3">
						<button>立即購買</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr />



	<div class="row">

		@* 產品特色介紹 *@
		<div class="col-6">
			<div class="detail-title text-center">
				<h1 class="detail-title-introduction">Introduction</h1>
				<small class="detail-title-small">商品特色</small>
			</div>
			<br />
			<p style="font-size: 14px;color:rgba(41, 52, 80, 0.8);font-style: italic;text-align: center">源自自然，匠心烘焙，從產地到口感，每項特色皆為打造精品咖啡的標準。</p>
			
			
			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header">&nbsp;產地</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">巴西</span>
					<span class="badge bg-success">哥倫比亞</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">印尼</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">衣索比亞</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">肯亞</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header">&nbsp;烘焙程度</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">淺焙</span>
					<span class="badge bg-success roast-level-answer">中淺焙</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">中焙</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">中深焙</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark thisanswer">深焙</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header">&nbsp;風味</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<span class="badge bg-success">白花</span>
					<span class="badge bg-success">檸檬草</span>
					<span class="badge bg-success">佛手柑</span>
					<span class="badge bg-success">甘蔗</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header">&nbsp;處理法</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<span class="badge bg-success">蜜處理</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">日曬</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">水洗</span>
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">半水洗</span><br />
					<span class="badge bg-success">結合了水洗與日曬，甜感飽滿、細緻酒香</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header">&nbsp;商品規格</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">重 量</span>
					<span class="badge bg-success">2 0 0 g</span><br />
					<span class="badge bg-light text-dark">保存期限</span>
					<span class="badge bg-success">1 2 個月</span>
				</div>
			</div>


			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header">&nbsp;味道分布</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					@* <p>味道分布圖</p> *@
					<canvas id="polarAreaChart" style="width: 60%"></canvas>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>


		@* 手沖咖啡計算機 *@
		<div class="col-6">
			<div class="detail-title text-center">
				<h1 class="detail-title-howtouse">How to use</h1>
				<small class="detail-title-small">匠人沖煮計算器</small>
			</div>
			<br />
			<p style="font-size: 14px;color:rgba(41, 52, 80, 0.8);font-style: italic;text-align: center">想沖出一杯理想的咖啡？簡單設定咖啡量與口感偏好，精準計算，帶您體驗專業咖啡師的沖煮感受！</p>
			
			
			@* 參數設定區 *@
			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header">參數設定</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					<div class="input-group mb-3" >
						<label class="input-group-text" for="inputGroupSelect01">咖啡飲用量</label>
						<select class="form-select text-center cooffee-drink-select" id="inputGroupSelect01" onchange="Select_Choose()">
							<option selected disabled>請選擇</option>
							<option value="50">一口飲</option>
							<option value="250">小酌</option>
							<option value="500">暢飲</option>
							<option value="other">其它</option>
						</select>
						<input type="number" class="form-control text-center coffee-drink-input" aria-label="Text input with dropdown button" disabled>
						<span class="input-group-text">毫升</span>
					</div>
					客製化選項:
					<div class="input-group mb-3">
						<label class="input-group-text" for="inputGroupSelect01">口味偏好</label>
						<select class="form-select text-center" id="inputGroupSelect01">
							<option selected>正常</option>
							<option value="1">酸多一點</option>
							<option value="2">苦多一點</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div class="input-group mb-3">
						<label class="input-group-text" for="inputGroupSelect01">濃厚偏好</label>
						<select class="form-select text-center" id="inputGroupSelect01">
							<option selected>正常</option>
							<option value="1">淡一點</option>
							<option value="2">濃一點</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div>
						<button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width:100%" onclick="calculateParameters()">開始計算</button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<br />
			@* 計算結果區 *@
			<div class="card border-light mb-3">
				<div class="card-header Aicoffee-blank-revision">推薦沖煮數據</div>
				<div class="card-body">
					@* 第一排 (水量、咖啡粉、沖煮時間) *@
					<div class="row Aicoffee-blank-revision">
						<div class="col-4">
							<div class="gaugeChart" id="waterChart"></div>
							<div class="Aicoffee-result-title-6">
								<img src="~/img/水量.png">
								<span>水量</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-4">
							<div class="gaugeChart" id="coffeeWeightChart"></div>
							<div class="Aicoffee-result-title-6">
								<img src="~/img/咖啡粉.png">
								<span>咖啡粉</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-4">
							<div class="gaugeChart" id="brewTimeChart"></div>
							<div class="Aicoffee-result-title-6">
								<img src="~/img/沖煮時間.png">
								<span>沖煮時間</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						@* 第二排(水溫、悶蒸水量、悶煮時間) *@
						<div class="col-4">
							<div class="gaugeChart" id="waterTemperatureChart"></div>
							<div class="Aicoffee-result-title-6">
								<img src="~/img/水溫.png">
								<span>水溫</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-4">
							<div class="gaugeChart" id="simmerWaterChart"></div>
							<div class="Aicoffee-result-title-6">
								<img src="~/img/悶蒸水量.png">
								<span>悶蒸水量</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="col-4">
							<div class="gaugeChart" id="simmerTimeChart"></div>
							<div class="Aicoffee-result-title-6">
								<img src="~/img/悶蒸時間.png">
								<span>悶蒸時間</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<br />
					<hr />
					@* 第四排( 研磨粗細 ) *@
					<div>
						&nbsp;<label>研磨粗細</label>
						<p class="Aicoffee-result-title-3 grind-size-result"></p>
					</div>
					@* 第五排( 萃取係數 ) *@
					<div>
						&nbsp;<label>萃取係數</label>
						<p class="Aicoffee-result-title-3 extraction-conditions-result"></p>
					</div>
					@* 第六排( 注水方式 ) *@
					<div>
						&nbsp;<label>注水方式</label>
						<p class="Aicoffee-result-title-3 add-water-result"></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<hr />
	<div>
		<ul>
			<li>為確保咖啡豆新鮮度及食品安全衛生考量，官網恕不提供代客研磨之服務，造成不便，敬請見諒。</li>
			<li>咖啡豆本身含有油脂，在烘焙時，咖啡豆會漸漸膨脹裂開，油脂會逐漸浮現到表面，而咖啡豆烘焙完後會
				產生二氧化碳並持續將油脂推出，故烘焙後數個月的期間表面會有出油狀態，尤其在中焙、深焙咖啡豆出
				油情況會更明顯，屬於正常現象。</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

</body>
